类 SynchronizedStack<T>

    直接已知子类:
    AbstractProtocol.RecycledProcessors

    public class SynchronizedStack<T>
extends Object
    This is intended as a (mostly) GC-free alternative to ConcurrentLinkedQueue when the requirement is to create a pool of re-usable objects with no requirement to shrink the pool. The aim is to provide the bare minimum of required functionality as quickly as possible with minimum garbage.
